- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes a method based on Generative Adversarial Nets (GAN) to improve detection accuracy.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with improving the accuracy of an AI model for object detection.
- cs.GR (Graphics) is a possible category as the paper deals with image processing and perturbation methods to enhance the dataset.
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper deals with image and object detection in multimedia datasets.
